== Uwera Pelagie ==
Uwera Pelagie yavutse mu mwaka wi 1974 ni umunyapolitiki wu munyarwandakazi kuva mu mwaka

wa 2019 akaba numwe mubagize sena yu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] yatorewe kuba sensteri [[Intara y'amajyepfo|Muntara y'amajyepfo]]

ku itariki ya 13 ugushyingo 2019 nibwo sens yu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]] yatoye umusensteri Pelagie Uwera 

kugirango ahagararire [[inteko ishinga amategeko]] yu [[Rwanda]] mu [[Inteko Ishinga Amategeko y’u Rwanda|nteko ishinga amategeko]] ya

Pan Africa ( PAP )<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/senators-uwera-bideri-represent-rwanda-pan-african-parliament</ref> ninzego zishinga amategeko zubumwe bw'Afurika yunze Ubumwe  (AU).

== Imirimo ==
Pelagie na Mugenziwe Bideri biyemeje guharanira iterambere nimibereho myiza y'[[Afurika]]

mu guhangana nubushomeri nubukene ndetse n'umutekano muke. bikaba biri no

mumpamvu abanyafurika bafata ingendo za hato nahato zo kujya mubihugo by' [[Iburayi]]

injyendo zishobora no guteza akaga bajya gushaka Imibereho myiza.<ref>https://www.parliament.gov.rw/senate-2/organs/assessment-committee</ref>

== Amashuri yize ==
Uwera Pelagie afite impamyabumenyi ihanitse munyigisho ziterambere ( Development studies ) <ref>https://clarifiedby.diligenciagroup.com/company/summary/4317038-uwera-pelagie/</ref>

akagira Impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu bumenyi bw'imibereho yakuye muri Kaminuza yijyenga ya [[Kigali]].

== Inshingano ==
Kuva mu mwaka 2012 kugeza 2019 Pelagie yari comiseri wa [[Komisiyo y’Igihugu yo Kurwanya SIDA|komisiyo y'Igihugu]] ishinzwe amatota

mu Rwanda. yabaye kandi Indorerezi y'Impuguke za <b>Commonwealth</b> mu matora rusange ya <b>[[Botswana|Botsuwana]]</b>

2014. muri 2018 yongera kuba Indorerezi ya <b>Commonwealth</b> mu matora Rusange ya <b>[[Siyera Lewone]] </b><ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/202107280775.html</ref> 

== Ibindi ==
Uwera Pelagie kandi yabaye umwarimu mu mashuri yisumbuye.

